      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，把HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault作为起始节点。那它首先连接到什么？是直接进入分析环节吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用户通过Vault触发HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，这是A1节点。同时助手端有个HealthTech_PatientRecords作为上下文输入，也连到A1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U",
        "A1",
