      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "如果D1是Yes，走C1节点HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，然后直接回到U结束。如果是No，进入A2 HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine做深度诊断。",
